comment._content: this is a Yokosuka D3Y myojo (Venus) which was a version of the Aichi type 99 made from wood. it had straight tapered wings because the original Typee 99 shape was too complex for unskilled workers Powered by a Mitubishi 1300hp Kinsei. Only two were built.
